introduction-tutorial-name = First steps on the station
introduction-tutorial-tooltip = A guide for beginners.
examine-something = Examine an item [tutkeybind="UIClick"/]

base-tutorial-sender = Instructor:
tutorial-base-step-examine-bubble = Examine the item. Use [tutkeybind="ExamineEntity"].
tutorial-base-step-examine-chat = Great! Let's start by examining items.
tutorial-base-step-examine-tts = Great! Let's start by examining items.
tutorial-base-step-pickup-bubble = Pick up the item.
tutorial-base-step-pickup-chat = Pick up the item to hold it in your hand.
tutorial-base-step-pickup-tts = Pick up the item to hold it in your hand.
tutorial-base-step-activate-action-chat = Activate the button with an icon on the action panel, either on the left or at the top.
tutorial-base-step-activate-action-tts = Activate the action.
tutorial-base-step-use-bubble = Use the item in your hand. Press [tutkeybind="UseItemInHand"].
tutorial-base-step-use-chat = Now use the item in your hand.
tutorial-base-step-use-tts = Now use the item in your hand.
tutorial-base-step-equip-bubble = Equip the item into a clothing slot.
tutorial-base-step-equip-chat = Drag the item onto yourself to wear it.
tutorial-base-step-equip-tts = Drag the item onto yourself to wear it.
tutorial-base-step-drop-bubble = Drop the item on the floor with [tutkeybind="Drop"].
tutorial-base-step-drop-chat = Drop the item from your hand.
tutorial-base-step-drop-tts = Drop the item from your hand.
tutorial-base-step-interact-chat = Interact with the object.
tutorial-base-step-interact-tts = Interact with the object.
tutorial-base-step-reach-chat = Reach the marked location.
tutorial-base-step-reach-tts = Reach the marked location.
tutorial-base-step-attack-bubble = Hit any item or wall.
tutorial-base-step-attack-chat = Try attacking.
tutorial-base-step-attack-tts = Try attacking.
tutorial-base-walk-bubble = Walk around a little. Use [tutkeybind="MoveUp"] [tutkeybind="MoveLeft"] [tutkeybind="MoveDown"] [tutkeybind="MoveRight"].
tutorial-base-walk-chat = Walk around a little to get used to movement.
tutorial-base-walk-tts = Walk around a little to get used to movement.

# --- Introduction Tutorial strings ---

intro-tut-walk-bubble = Walk around a little. Use [tutkeybind="MoveUp"] [tutkeybind="MoveLeft"] [tutkeybind="MoveDown"] [tutkeybind="MoveRight"].

intro-tut-go-locker-room-bubble = Go to the locker room. Follow the mark on the floor.
intro-tut-go-locker-room-chat = Welcome aboard our small space station! Let's go into the locker room first and pick out some clothes.
intro-tut-go-locker-room-tts = Welcome aboard our small space station! Let's go into the locker room first and pick out some clothes.

intro-tut-examine-clothing-vendor-bubble = Examine the clothing vendor [tutkeybind="ExamineEntity"].
intro-tut-examine-clothing-vendor-chat = Before using an unfamiliar object, you can examine it. This often tells you what it is and what to do with it.
intro-tut-examine-clothing-vendor-tts = Before using an unfamiliar object, you can examine it. This often tells you what it is and what to do with it.

intro-tut-open-clothing-vendor-bubble = Open the clothing vendor [tutkeybind="UIClick"].
intro-tut-open-clothing-vendor-chat = Now interact with the vendor. Many objects on the station have their own window with buttons, items, or settings.
intro-tut-open-clothing-vendor-tts = Now interact with the vendor. Many objects on the station have their own window with buttons, items, or settings.

intro-tut-take-clothing-bubble = Take the beret from the vendor. Press [tutkeybind="UIClick"] on the needed item.
intro-tut-take-clothing-chat = In the open vendor, choose the beret. The item will appear in your hand.
intro-tut-take-clothing-tts = In the open vendor, choose the beret. The item will appear in your hand.

intro-tut-hold-beret-bubble = Hold the beret in your hand. If it is not in your hands, click it in the inventory or pick it up from the floor.
intro-tut-hold-beret-chat = Before you wear something, it should be in your hand. Hold the beret in your active hand.
intro-tut-hold-beret-tts = Before you wear something, it should be in your hand. Hold the beret in your active hand.

intro-tut-equip-clothing-bubble = Put on the beret. Open the inventory with [tutkeybind="OpenInventoryMenu"] and drag the item into the right slot, or press [tutkeybind="ActivateItemInHand"] to equip it quickly.
intro-tut-equip-clothing-chat = Put on the cool beret. It suits you.
intro-tut-equip-clothing-tts = Put on the cool beret. It suits you.

intro-tut-drop-old-clothing-bubble = Drop the old clothing item on the floor with [tutkeybind="Drop"].
intro-tut-drop-old-clothing-chat = The old clothing is now in your hand. Just drop it.
intro-tut-drop-old-clothing-tts = The old clothing is now in your hand. Just drop it.

intro-tut-swap-hands-bubble = You have two hands! Press [tutkeybind="SwapHands"] to switch your active hand.
intro-tut-swap-hands-chat = The game has two hands. You can hold items in both and switch between them quickly.
intro-tut-swap-hands-tts = The game has two hands. You can hold items in both and switch between them quickly.

intro-tut-left-status-panel-bubble = The left status panel shows the state of the item in your left hand.
intro-tut-left-status-panel-chat = There is a status panel to the left of your hands. If an item can show something like charge, fuel, or mode, it appears there.
intro-tut-left-status-panel-tts = There is a status panel to the left of your hands. If an item can show something like charge, fuel, or mode, it appears there.

intro-tut-inventory-bubble = This is the inventory. Open it with [tutkeybind="OpenInventoryMenu"] to see clothes, pockets, belt, and backpack.
intro-tut-inventory-chat = Inventory is not just a bag. You use it to wear clothes, move items, and check what you are wearing.
intro-tut-inventory-tts = Inventory is not just a bag. You use it to wear clothes, move items, and check what you are wearing.

intro-tut-go-center-bubble = Go to the center of the location. Follow the marker.
intro-tut-go-center-chat = Great! Now move to the central hall.
intro-tut-go-center-tts = Great! Now move to the central hall.

intro-tut-go-bar-bubble = Head to the bar. Follow the marker.
intro-tut-go-bar-chat = Take a look at the bar. You can catch your breath, drink something, and have a good time there.
intro-tut-go-bar-tts = Take a look at the bar. You can catch your breath, drink something, and have a good time there.

intro-tut-sit-chair-bubble = Sit on the bar stool with [tutkeybind="UIClick"] on the chair.
intro-tut-sit-chair-chat = Click the nearest stool to sit down.
intro-tut-sit-chair-tts = Click the stool to sit down.

intro-tut-pickup-drink-bubble = Pick up the glass of orange juice from the counter with [tutkeybind="UIClick"].
intro-tut-pickup-drink-chat = There is orange juice on the counter. Take it!
intro-tut-pickup-drink-tts = There is orange juice on the counter. Take it!

intro-tut-drink-bubble = Drink the juice with [tutkeybind="ActivateItemInHand"].
intro-tut-drink-chat = Hold the glass in your hand and activate it to drink.
intro-tut-drink-tts = Hold the glass in your hand and activate it to drink.

intro-tut-go-bar-counter-bubble = Go behind the counter. Follow the marker.
intro-tut-go-bar-counter-chat = I wonder what is behind the counter... You should check and go behind it.
intro-tut-go-bar-counter-tts = I wonder what is behind the counter... You should check and go behind it.

intro-tut-examine-airlock-bubble = Examine the service airlock [tutkeybind="ExamineEntity"].
intro-tut-examine-airlock-chat = Looks like this airlock is locked. You cannot pass without access.
intro-tut-examine-airlock-tts = Looks like this airlock is locked. You cannot pass without access.

intro-tut-rummage-bush-bubble = Rummage through the nearby bush with [tutkeybind="UIClick"].
intro-tut-rummage-bush-chat = Something is hidden in the bushes. You should check!
intro-tut-rummage-bush-tts = Something is hidden in the bushes. You should check!

intro-tut-equip-id-card-bubble = Insert the access card into the ID slot with [tutkeybind="UIClick"] on the ID card slot.
intro-tut-equip-id-card-chat = While holding a card or wearing it in its special slot, you can pass through locked doors.
intro-tut-equip-id-card-tts = The access card opens service doors. Useful!

intro-tut-pass-airlock-bubble = Hold the access card in your hand and pass through the airlock with [tutkeybind="ActivateItemInWorld"].
intro-tut-pass-airlock-chat = The access card opens some locked doors. Hold it in your hand to pass.
intro-tut-pass-airlock-tts = The access card opens some locked doors. Hold it in your hand to pass.

intro-tut-open-dresser-bubble = Open the dresser with [tutkeybind="UIClick"].
intro-tut-open-dresser-chat = Open the dresser. Maybe there is something interesting inside!
intro-tut-open-dresser-tts = Open the dresser. Maybe there is something interesting inside!

intro-tut-go-back-center-bubble = Return to the central hall.
intro-tut-go-back-center-chat = Well, this place is empty. Return to the center.
intro-tut-go-back-center-tts = Well, this place is empty. Return to the center, then we will go to another room.

intro-tut-go-hallway-bubble = Move toward the next corridor.
intro-tut-go-hallway-chat = Hmm... something is wrong ahead. The lights are off. Check what is there.
intro-tut-go-hallway-tts = Hmm... something is wrong ahead. The lights are off. Check what is there.

intro-tut-pickup-flashlight-bubble = It is dark here! Pick up the flashlight with [tutkeybind="UIClick"].
intro-tut-pickup-flashlight-chat = Yeah, that is dark! Pick up the flashlight to light the way.
intro-tut-pickup-flashlight-tts = Yeah, that is dark! Pick up the flashlight to light the way.

intro-tut-turn-on-flashlight-bubble = Turn on the flashlight with [tutkeybind="ActivateItemInHand"].
intro-tut-turn-on-flashlight-chat = Activate the item in your hand to turn on the flashlight.
intro-tut-turn-on-flashlight-tts = Activate the item in your hand to turn on the flashlight.

intro-tut-go-range-bubble = Move to the training range.
intro-tut-go-range-chat = There is a training range ahead. Time to practice.
intro-tut-go-range-tts = There is a training range ahead. Time to practice.

intro-tut-try-open-bolted-bubble = Try to open the airlock with [tutkeybind="UIClick"].
intro-tut-try-open-bolted-chat = The door is bolted! Try to remove the lock by pressing the airlock.
intro-tut-try-open-bolted-tts = The door is bolted! Try to remove the lock by pressing the airlock.

intro-tut-press-button-bubble = Press the nearby signal button with [tutkeybind="UIClick"].
intro-tut-press-button-chat = A bolted door has red lights and cannot be opened with a card. Good thing there is a button here that unlocks it.
intro-tut-press-button-tts = A bolted door has red lights and cannot be opened with a card. Good thing there is a button here that unlocks it.

intro-tut-pickup-pistol-bubble = Pick up the training laser pistol with [tutkeybind="UIClick"].
intro-tut-pickup-pistol-chat = Here is the range. A great chance to practice shooting. Take the pistol!
intro-tut-pickup-pistol-tts = Here is the range. A great chance to practice shooting. Take the pistol!

intro-tut-action-bar-bubble = This is the action bar. Character abilities and quick actions appear here.
intro-tut-action-bar-chat = The action bar is useful for combat mode and abilities. If a new button appears, it is probably worth checking.
intro-tut-action-bar-tts = The action bar is useful for combat mode and abilities. If a new button appears, it is probably worth checking.

intro-tut-combat-mode-bubble = Enter combat mode: press the highlighted button on the action bar or [tutkeybind="Num1"].
intro-tut-combat-mode-chat = To attack with a weapon, you need to enter combat mode. Press the highlighted button or number 1.
intro-tut-combat-mode-tts = To attack with a weapon, you need to enter combat mode. Press the highlighted button or number 1.

intro-tut-shoot-bubble = Shoot the targets 3 times with [tutkeybind="UIClick"] on a target.
intro-tut-shoot-chat = Aim at the targets and open fire!
intro-tut-shoot-tts = Aim at the targets and open fire!

intro-tut-pickup-knife-bubble = Pick up the survival knife with [tutkeybind="UIClick"].
intro-tut-pickup-knife-chat = Now let's practice melee combat. Take the knife from the shelf.
intro-tut-pickup-knife-tts = Now let's practice melee combat. Take the knife from the shelf.

intro-tut-attack-clown-bubble = Attack the clown target with [tutkeybind="UIClick"].
intro-tut-attack-clown-chat = Hit the clown target. Serves it right!
intro-tut-attack-clown-tts = Hit the clown target. Serves it right!

intro-tut-drop-drink-bubble = Put the glass back with [tutkeybind="Drop"].
intro-tut-drop-drink-chat = Remember to put the glass back. Stealing glasses is not accepted at the bar.
intro-tut-drop-drink-tts = Remember to put the glass back. Stealing glasses is not accepted at the bar.

intro-tut-drop-id-card-bubble = Drop the access card with [tutkeybind="Drop"]. You will not need it anymore.
intro-tut-drop-id-card-chat = We will not need the card anymore. Drop it.
intro-tut-drop-id-card-tts = We will not need the card anymore. Drop it.

intro-tut-store-flashlight-bubble = Put the flashlight into your backpack or drop it with [tutkeybind="Drop"] before shooting.
intro-tut-store-flashlight-chat = Free your hands before taking a weapon.
intro-tut-store-flashlight-tts = Free your hands before taking a weapon.
